c: 6
v: 54
t: "When those who believe in Our revelations come to (visit) you say, \"Assalam Alaikum (peace upon you)\". Your Lord has decreed mercy (and compassion) upon Himself. Indeed, if any one of you commits a wrong deed (by mistake and) out of ignorance and thereafter repents and mends his ways, (he would find that) He is the most Forgiving and the most Merciful"